# Rust build artifacts
/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# ts-rs intermediate per-type .d.ts output (#1218 Phase 1).
# `scripts/regen-ts-bindings.sh` writes per-type files here as
# generator scratch, then concatenates them into
# `crates/rustledger-wasm/bindings/index.d.ts` which IS checked in
# (it's the canonical TS API surface; CI gates its freshness via
# `RUSTLEDGER_TS_CHECK=1 scripts/regen-ts-bindings.sh`).
crates/rustledger-wasm/bindings/bindings/

